Actions.Name: Get cube by ID
Actions.Description: Get the cube with the given ID in the given database. To prevent issues with the URL encodings, Attribute cubes will be renamed, e.g. #_Years to ATT_Years.

Actions.Name: Get cube cells
Actions.Description: Get the cells from a cube. This returns the cells' values and element names. If the cell has a string value, the value is instead stored in the stringValue field. Element names are stored in dynamic properties.

Actions.Name: Get cubes
Actions.Description: Get a list of cubes in the given database. To prevent issues with the URL encodings, Attribute cubes will be renamed, e.g. #_Years to ATT_Years.

Actions.Name: Get database by id
Actions.Description: Get the database with the given ID.

Actions.Name: Get databases
Actions.Description: Get a list of databases found in the server. System and config databases are excluded from the list, but can be requested by providing the ID.

Actions.Name: Get dimension by ID
Actions.Description: Get the dimension with the given ID in the given database.

Actions.Name: Get dimensions
Actions.Description: Get a list of dimensions in the given database.

Actions.Name: Get element by ID
Actions.Description: Returns the element with the given ID in the given dimension.

Actions.Name: Get elements
Actions.Description: Get a list of elements in the given dimension.

Actions.Name: Get extract by Name
Actions.Description: Get the extract with the given name in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get extract rows
Actions.Description: Stream the rows of the extract with the given name in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get extracts
Actions.Description: Get a list of extracts in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get Integrator project groups
Actions.Description: Get a list of integrator project groups found in the server.

Actions.Name: Get Integrator projects
Actions.Description: Get a list of integrator projects found in the server.

Actions.Name: Get Integrator project group by identifier
Actions.Description: Get the project group with the given ID.

Actions.Name: Get Integrator project by name
Actions.Description: Get the integrator project with the given name.

Actions.Name: Get job by name
Actions.Description: Get the jobs with the given name in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get jobs
Actions.Description: Get a list of jobs in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get load by name
Actions.Description: Get the transform with the given name in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get loads
Actions.Description: Get a list of loads in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Run job
Actions.Description: Run the job with the given name in the given integrator project. The execution will be added to the queue.

Actions.Name: Run job with variables
Actions.Description: Run the job with the given name in the given integrator project. The execution will be added to the queue.

Actions.Name: Run load
Actions.Description: Run the load with the given name in the given integrator project. The execution will be added to the queue.

Actions.Name: Run load with variables
Actions.Description: Run the load with the given name in the given integrator project. The execution will be added to the queue.

Actions.Name: Get transform by name
Actions.Description: Get the transform with the given name in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get transform Rows
Actions.Description: Stream the rows of the transform with the given name in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get transforms
Actions.Description: Get a list of transforms in the given integrator project.

Actions.Name: Get stored view by ID
Actions.Description: Get the view with the given ID in the given database.

Actions.Name: Get stored view cells
Actions.Description: Get all cells from a view. This returns the cells' values and element names. If the cell has a string value, the value is instead stored in the stringValue field. Element names are stored in dynamic properties.

Actions.Name: Get stored views
Actions.Description: Get a list of stored views in the given database.
